00:18:12,725 --> 00:18:14,226
JULIA!

261
00:18:16,262 --> 00:18:17,730
JULIA!

262
00:18:17,730 --> 00:18:19,498
JULIA?

263
00:18:19,498 --> 00:18:20,466
MR. DANKER.

264
00:18:20,466 --> 00:18:22,902
YOU'RE BACK EARLY.

265
00:18:22,902 --> 00:18:24,704
