1099
01:16:44,133 --> 01:16:47,937
TODAY. ALONE.

1100
01:16:47,937 --> 01:16:51,407
NO MONEY. NO CLOTHES.

1101
01:16:51,407 --> 01:16:52,908
ALONE.

1102
01:16:52,908 --> 01:16:56,378
ONE HUNDRED PERCENT ALONE.

1103
01:16:56,378 --> 01:16:58,781
NOW...

