01:27:03,418 --> 01:27:05,887
THE GAME IS OVER.

1228
01:27:05,887 --> 01:27:07,889
( Teddy groans )
 TAKE IT EASY.

1229
01:27:11,660 --> 01:27:14,596
TAKE IT EASY.

1230
01:27:14,596 --> 01:27:15,831
BETTER GET AN AMBULANCE.

1231
01:27:15,831 --> 01:27:17,065
FORGET ABOUT THE AMBULANCE.

1232
01:27:17,065 --> 01:27:19,801
