I NEVER WANTED JIMMY RAY

1239
01:27:39,721 --> 01:27:41,389
TO GET TO YOU.

1240
01:27:41,389 --> 01:27:44,726
PLEASE BELIEVE THAT.

1241
01:27:44,726 --> 01:27:51,132
YOU KNOW, THAT DARKNESS IN
THE LIGHT--IT'S ALL MY FAULT.

1242
01:27:51,132 --> 01:27:54,135
IT'S MY FAULT. MY FAULT.

1243
01:27:54,135 --> 01:27:56,071
JUST DON'T TALK ANYMORE.

1244
01:27:56,071 --> 01:27:57,372
COME ON.

1245
01:27:57,372 --> 01:28:01,042
OKAY, GET HIM UP.

1246
01:28:01,042 --> 01:28:02,944
( groaning )
 EASY.

1247
01:28:08,783 --> 01:28:10,552
GOT HIS LEG?

1248
01:28:10,552 --> 01:28:13,655
( siren wails )
 I'M GOING WITH YOU.

1249
01:28:13,655 --> 01:28:14,856
