1274
01:29:28,029 --> 01:29:31,099
YOU FELT SORRY FOR ME?

1275
01:29:31,099 --> 01:29:36,137
DON'T YOU MEAN YOU WERE
OBSESSED WITH ME?

1276
01:29:36,137 --> 01:29:38,807
ISN'T THAT WHAT YOU MEAN?

1277
01:29:38,807 --> 01:29:42,177
THAT YOU WERE OBSESSED WITH ME
AND YOU COULDN'T STAND IT THAT

1278
01:29:42,177 --> 01:29:45,647
I STAYED WITH JIMMY RAY?

1279
